div.p:
                  Edward Burroughs (ſtiled a Son of Thunder, and Conſolation; a true Prophet, and faithful Servant of God, in his Works Reprinted 1672.) p. 149. has an Anſwer to this Queſtion;
'Is that very Man, with that very Body within you, Yea or Nay?' He ſaith,
'The very Chriſt of God is within us, we dare not deny him.'
